WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.935 align:middle line:90%


00:00:05.935 --> 00:00:07.810 align:middle line:10%
>>REPORTER: The US
military has launched what

00:00:07.810 --> 00:00:10.450 align:middle line:10%
many have mistaken for a UFO.

00:00:10.450 --> 00:00:15.670 align:middle line:10%
It's a new unmanned drone
aircraft called the X-47B.

00:00:15.670 --> 00:00:18.970 align:middle line:10%
The US Navy plans to use it
for sea-based attack missions

00:00:18.970 --> 00:00:21.010 align:middle line:10%
without the use of a pilot.

00:00:21.010 --> 00:00:22.810 align:middle line:10%
Test flights are
scheduled to take place

00:00:22.810 --> 00:00:25.390 align:middle line:10%
over the coming weeks from
an aircraft carrier stationed

00:00:25.390 --> 00:00:27.130 align:middle line:10%
off the East Coast.

00:00:27.130 --> 00:00:30.430 align:middle line:10%
The drone is controlled
completely through computers.

00:00:30.430 --> 00:00:33.730 align:middle line:10%
It can carry two
2,000-pound bombs.

00:00:33.730 --> 00:00:37.260 align:middle line:10%
The estimated cost is
around $813 million.

00:00:37.260 --> 00:00:40.240 align:middle line:10%
The program has received
criticism for its price tag,

00:00:40.240 --> 00:00:43.440 align:middle line:10%
and over the ethics
of drone warfare.

00:00:43.440 --> 00:00:50.000 align:middle line:90%